1. INTRODUCTION
Ashoka Power Matrix Pvt. Ltd. is a leading electrical manufacturing enterprise specializing in engineering excellence and robust machinery assemblies. With over 25 years of excellence, we design and manufacture high-efficiency power distribution units and smart grid panels.

2. CORE PRODUCTS
- Current Transformers (CTs)
- Potential Transformers (PTs)
- Metering Solutions
- Control Panels
- Accessories

3. QUALITY COMPLIANCE
Every product undergoes rigid short-circuit and insulation safety testing, fully complying with IS and IEC standards.
